                    />

            
    
<figcaption class="attribution">
        <span class="attribution__caption">Kenneth Nixon, who was wrongfully imprisoned for nearly 16 years, is renovating property he purchased in Detroit into an adult foster care home.</span>
    
    
    
    </figcaption>

</figure>

        
    
                        

