                    />

            
    
<figcaption class="attribution">
        <span class="attribution__caption">From left: Anthony Legion, Eric Anderson, Marvin Cotton Jr., Ronnell Johnson and Alexandre Ansari listen as Organization of Exonerees President Kenneth Nixon introduces them during the group’s gala and fundraiser.</span>
    
    
    
