    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/illinois-judge-closes-franklin-county-juvenile-detention-center-failed-to-meet-state-standards">
                                    Illinois Judge Closes Juvenile Detention Center After “Facility in Crisis” Fails to Meet New State Standards
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            The Franklin County Juvenile Detention Center abruptly closed on Dec. 31. The judge who ordered the closure said staffing shortages made it difficult to meet state standards for caring for youth in custody.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <span class="name">Molly Parker</span>, <a href="https://capitolnewsillinois.com/">Capitol News Illinois</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-01-04EST11:00">Jan. 4, 11 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

                <p class="story-card__unit">Local Reporting Network</p>
            </div>
