            </a>
        </div>
    
    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/body-camera-videos-police-killings-remain-hidden-from-public">
                                    Body Cameras Were Sold as a Tool of Police Reform. Ten Years Later, Most of the Footage Is Kept From Public View.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            There were 101 people killed at the hands of police in June 2022. More than a year later, police had released body-camera footage of only 33 of those killings, ProPublica has found.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/umar-farooq">Umar Farooq</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2023-12-18EST05:00">Dec. 18, 2023, 5 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    

                    
                    
    
        <div class="lead-art">
            <a class="aspect-3-2" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/utah-women-tried-to-report-their-sexual-assaults-to-police-they-say-they-faced-delays-and-language-barriers">
                <img
